    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h2>Android Studio Arctic Fox (2020.3.1)</h2>\n<p>In Android Studio Arctic Fox (2020.3.1 Patch 4), the JDK Location setting is moved to:</p>\n<pre><code>File &gt; Settings &gt; Build, Execution, Deployment &gt; Build Tools &gt; Gradle &gt; Gradle JDK\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Up to Android Studio 4.2</h2>\n<p>You can follow the answer from Ben Kane, the JDK Location setting is located in:</p>\n<pre><code>File &gt; Project Structure &gt; SDK Location\n</code></pre>\n"
